T1  - MANAGING INEQUALITY OVER BUSINESS CYCLES: OPTIMAL POLICIES WITH HETEROGENEOUS AGENTS AND AGGREGATE SHOCKS
AU  - Le Grand, François
AU  - Ragot, Xavier
Y1  - 2022/02/01
PY  - 2022
